data.description: Attention investors and renovation enthusiasts! Property is located on the Palmetto Pine Country Club golf course, short distance to Club House and Driving range. This residential home is being sold as-is, offering the chance for a complete renovation and customization to your liking. Open canvas interior allowing for endless design possibilities.  Please note that the seller will not be making any repairs to the property. This is a unique opportunity for investors and buyers with a keen eye for renovation projects. Bring your contractor and explore the potential that this property holds. Embrace the challenge and rewards of a complete renovation project in a prime Cape Coral location. Don't miss out on this chance to transform a property into a masterpiece.
